## 广度优先遍历 bfs
```java
public void bfs(Node node){
    if(node == null){
        return;
    }
    Queue<Node> queue = new LinkedList<>();
    HashSet<Node> set = new HashSet<>();

    queue.add(node);
    set.add(node);
    while (!queue.isEmpty()){
        Node cur = queue.poll();
        System.out.println(cur.value);
        for(Node next: cur.next){
            if(!set.contains(next)){
                queue.add(next);
                set.add(next);
            }
        }
    }
}
```
