## 深度优先遍历 dfs
```java
public void dfs(Node node){
    if(node == null){
        return;
    }

    Stack<Node> stack = new Stack<>();
    HashSet<Node> set = new HashSet<>();
    stack.add(node);
    set.add(node);
    System.out.println(node.value);
    while (!stack.isEmpty()){
        Node cur = stack.pop();
        for(Node next: cur.next){
            if(!set.contains(next)){
                stack.push(cur);
                stack.push(next);
                set.add(next);
                System.out.println(next.value);
                break;
            }
        }
    }
}
```

